224
00:19:46,840 --> 00:19:47,880
I remember

225
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:50,680
before he was strangled to death,

226
00:19:51,680 --> 00:19:53,320
he was mumbling

227
00:19:54,760 --> 00:19:55,440
that he was fed up to the back teeth.

228
00:19:59,280 --> 00:19:59,840
Magistrate,

229
00:20:00,480 --> 00:20:02,280
I also grew up in Chang'an
since I was a child.

230
00:20:02,600 --> 00:20:03,240
After all,

231
00:20:03,320 --> 00:20:04,760
we can understand

232
00:20:04,760 --> 00:20:05,640
each other.

233
