238
00:20:35,360 --> 00:20:37,440
of these soldiers in Zhenxi Fortress.

239
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:39,040
Their native places,

240
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:40,600
enlistment time,

241
00:20:41,200 --> 00:20:42,760
