247
00:20:54,080 --> 00:20:54,760
A whip?

248
00:20:56,000 --> 00:20:56,640
Lash mark.

249
00:20:57,400 --> 00:20:57,960
Just now,

250
00:20:57,960 --> 00:20:59,320
