251
00:20:59,320 --> 00:21:00,200
on those soldiers.

252
00:21:00,800 --> 00:21:01,720
So

253
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:04,040
they were caused
by the three-section whip.

254
00:21:05,040 --> 00:21:07,760
No wonder the barracks are so dead.

255
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:10,360
Huo Huaili is so despicable.

256
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:12,720
But I think

257
00:21:13,120 --> 00:21:15,280
they respect Huo Huaili very much.

258
00:21:18,520 --> 00:21:19,480
Most of these soldiers

259
00:21:19,960 --> 00:21:21,280
