264
00:21:30,880 --> 00:21:32,360
Zhou Changyong.

265
00:21:32,920 --> 00:21:34,320
Zhou Changyi.

266
00:21:54,840 --> 00:21:56,080
What's hiding under there?

267
00:21:58,440 --> 00:21:59,400
Let's go take a look.

268
00:22:01,760 --> 00:22:02,720
Go over there to take a look.

269
00:23:40,080 --> 00:23:40,640
This...

270
00:23:41,400 --> 00:23:43,400
This is Huo Huaili's three-section whip?

271
00:23:44,920 --> 00:23:45,680
Magistrate Di,

272
00:23:47,280 --> 00:23:48,760
now that you've discovered it,

273
00:23:49,480 --> 00:23:50,640
please come out.

274
00:24:05,640 --> 00:24:07,560
What are you going to do with us?

275
00:24:09,080 --> 00:24:10,320
You will make up

276
00:24:10,760 --> 00:24:12,640
a reason that we stole horses
to cross the border.

277
00:24:13,000 --> 00:24:13,600
