284
00:24:32,400 --> 00:24:34,080
I killed Huo Huaili.

285
00:24:34,720 --> 00:24:35,600
Zhou Changyi.

286
00:24:35,820 --> 00:24:36,700
[Huo Huaili]

287
00:24:37,120 --> 00:24:38,480
