290
00:24:47,240 --> 00:24:48,600
So, you killed him.

291
00:24:49,960 --> 00:24:51,880
You incited a riot,

292
00:24:52,320 --> 00:24:53,840
offended your superior,

293
00:24:53,840 --> 00:24:55,200
and assumed his identity.

294
00:24:56,320 --> 00:24:57,120
According to the law,

295
00:24:58,520 --> 00:25:00,720
you should have been killed
several times.

296
00:25:26,440 --> 00:25:27,880
He did as he pleased.

297
00:25:30,200 --> 00:25:31,920
He beat us whenever he wanted.

298
00:25:34,080 --> 00:25:35,560
But that is called
training new soldiers.

299
00:25:36,760 --> 00:25:38,200
It was not a crime.

300
00:25:39,320 --> 00:25:40,840
When he was in a bad mood,

301
00:25:41,400 --> 00:25:43,040
he took it out on us soldiers.

302
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:45,640
This is called giving exhortations.

303
00:25:46,680 --> 00:25:48,200
It was not a crime, either.

304
00:25:52,040 --> 00:25:54,120
He beat my brother to death.

305
00:25:54,720 --> 00:25:56,840
But this is called accidental homicide.

306
00:26:00,320 --> 00:26:02,200
He still couldn't be convicted.

307
00:26:04,280 --> 00:26:05,560
We couldn't bear it.

308
00:26:06,600 --> 00:26:08,680
We had nowhere to complain.

309
00:26:09,640 --> 00:26:10,920
We were even punished by him.

310
00:26:10,920 --> 00:26:12,760
He locked us up for seven days
without giving us food or water.

311
00:26:15,600 --> 00:26:16,680
In order to survive,

312
00:26:17,720 --> 00:26:18,640
we had no choice

313
00:26:19,520 --> 00:26:21,040
but to kill him.

314
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:23,320
However,

315
00:26:23,960 --> 00:26:25,600
we have thus committed a heinous crime

316
00:26:26,360 --> 00:26:27,880
and should be sentenced to death.

317
00:26:28,760 --> 00:26:29,720
Magistrate Di,

318
00:26:32,040 --> 00:26:32,960
who does the law

319
00:26:33,880 --> 00:26:35,520
actually support?

320
00:26:36,360 --> 00:26:37,720
Whose law is this?

321
00:26:38,520 --> 00:26:39,680
If you want to arrest Changyi,

322
00:26:39,960 --> 00:26:41,120
kill me first!

323
00:26:41,720 --> 00:26:42,440
Don't move.

324
00:26:42,520 --> 00:26:43,480
Don't be silly.

325
00:26:44,640 --> 00:26:45,840
Don't move. Put down the knife.

326
00:27:02,800 --> 00:27:04,160
They just want to survive.

327
00:27:04,160 --> 00:27:05,320
They did nothing wrong.

328
00:27:07,200 --> 00:27:08,920
Huo Huaili deserved to die.

329
00:27:09,440 --> 00:27:10,240
I tell you,

330
00:27:10,880 --> 00:27:12,360
if I were a soldier here,

331
00:27:12,360 --> 00:27:13,320
I would do the same.

332
00:27:15,160 --> 00:27:15,840
Speak!

333
00:27:20,880 --> 00:27:21,840
Huo Huaili

334
00:27:23,440 --> 00:27:24,880
did deserve to die.

335
00:27:26,040 --> 00:27:29,600
But there are thousands of soldiers
guarding the borders of Tang.

336
00:27:29,880 --> 00:27:30,760
If they all mutinied

337
00:27:31,400 --> 00:27:32,880
and killed their officers

338
00:27:34,600 --> 00:27:37,040
because the latter

339
00:27:37,560 --> 00:27:38,960
were tyrannical,

340
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:42,240
the prosperity and stability of Tang

341
00:27:42,760 --> 00:27:44,520
would be lost.

342
00:27:46,040 --> 00:27:46,680
Well,

343
00:27:47,760 --> 00:27:48,640
what should we do

344
00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:51,720
at that time?

345
00:27:58,480 --> 00:27:59,480
Bravo.

346
00:28:01,000 --> 00:28:02,600
So high-sounding.

347
00:28:04,440 --> 00:28:05,240
You tell me

348
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:06,840
what they can do.

349
00:28:07,800 --> 00:28:08,840
They have no power.

350
00:28:09,400 --> 00:28:10,560
They can only wait for death?

351
00:28:11,600 --> 00:28:12,480
Cut the crap.

352
00:28:12,480 --> 00:28:13,320
Get us out of here first.

353
00:28:13,760 --> 00:28:14,480
Why?

354
00:28:15,240 --> 00:28:15,920
You...

355
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:19,240
The less you have to do

356
00:28:19,800 --> 00:28:20,840
in this world, the better.

357
00:28:23,240 --> 00:28:23,600
Fine.

358
00:28:23,920 --> 00:28:24,360
Okay.

359
00:28:25,000 --> 00:28:26,960
I'll tell those soldiers later

360
00:28:27,280 --> 00:28:28,880
that you are with us.

361
00:28:29,160 --> 00:28:30,400
Let them bring you in, too.

362
00:28:31,720 --> 00:28:32,320
Daguan,

363
00:28:33,280 --> 00:28:34,280
who don't you speak?

364
00:28:35,160 --> 00:28:36,160
You can't answer me?

365
00:28:39,080 --> 00:28:40,120
What Zhou Changyi did

366
00:28:40,800 --> 00:28:42,520
is very common in this world.

367
00:28:43,840 --> 00:28:45,520
There are also many people
like Han Yongnan.

368
00:28:46,400 --> 00:28:47,720
You didn't catch the ones
you should catch,

369
00:28:47,800 --> 00:28:48,840
but caught the ones you shouldn't.

370
00:28:49,480 --> 00:28:50,760
You stormed a hundred li

371
00:28:51,000 --> 00:28:52,640
and now your life is in danger.

372
00:28:53,480 --> 00:28:54,280
Is it worth it?

373
00:28:59,120 --> 00:29:01,040
Zhou Changyi incited a riot

374
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:03,440
and killed his officer.

375
00:29:04,080 --> 00:29:04,920
He deserves to die.

376
00:29:06,920 --> 00:29:08,760
Han Yongnan raped a young girl

377
00:29:09,600 --> 00:29:11,320
and broke the law of Tang.

378
00:29:12,280 --> 00:29:13,760
He also deserves to die.

379
00:29:14,600 --> 00:29:15,680
I, Di Renjie,

380
00:29:15,760 --> 00:29:17,400
am an official appointed by the court.

381
00:29:18,320 --> 00:29:20,040
I have to do this.

382
00:29:26,600 --> 00:29:28,840
You remind me of my father.

383
00:29:30,520 --> 00:29:31,960
He died of fever.

384
00:29:33,480 --> 00:29:35,440
I actually hoped he was killed by someone.

385
00:29:36,720 --> 00:29:38,240
That way, I could have an enemy.

386
00:29:38,840 --> 00:29:40,080
I could travel a long way
to seek revenge

387
00:29:40,240 --> 00:29:41,240
and kill the enemy to vent my hatred.

388
00:29:41,800 --> 00:29:43,000
I could feel better that way.

389
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:46,480
I catch Han Yongnan

390
00:29:46,520 --> 00:29:47,520
not to take revenge.

391
00:29:47,520 --> 00:29:49,440
I'll take him back to Lanfang County

392
00:29:49,440 --> 00:29:50,680
to stand trial.

393
00:29:50,960 --> 00:29:52,160
Yes.

394
00:29:52,360 --> 00:29:53,920
You will take him back
to your Magistrate's Office.

395
00:29:54,760 --> 00:29:55,640
It will also be you

396
00:29:55,640 --> 00:29:56,520
who will judge him

397
00:29:56,880 --> 00:29:57,720
and execute him.

398
00:29:58,240 --> 00:29:59,040
What's the difference?

399
00:30:06,280 --> 00:30:08,680
I don't understand your laws or rules,

400
00:30:09,840 --> 00:30:10,600
nor do I want to understand them.

401
00:30:11,600 --> 00:30:12,920
But I know

402
00:30:14,240 --> 00:30:15,720
all men, no matter how high or low,

403
00:30:16,000 --> 00:30:17,240
are beasts

404
00:30:17,600 --> 00:30:18,600
beneath the skin.

405
00:30:19,760 --> 00:30:21,360
It's just that some are domineering

406
00:30:21,560 --> 00:30:22,920
and some are trampled upon.

407
00:30:23,600 --> 00:30:25,840
Han Yongnan is a dhole in Lanfang County,

408
00:30:25,840 --> 00:30:27,080
showing his teeth.

409
00:30:28,280 --> 00:30:29,040
But in this place,

410
00:30:29,960 --> 00:30:31,360
he is not even a rat.

411
00:30:32,160 --> 00:30:33,840
He could be torn into pieces
at any time.

412
00:31:09,640 --> 00:31:10,400
There are bandits.

413
00:31:10,400 --> 00:31:11,280
The bandits are coming.

414
00:31:12,640 --> 00:31:13,840
The bandits are coming.

415
00:31:18,800 --> 00:31:19,320
What's the matter?

416
00:31:21,200 --> 00:31:21,680
Come here.

417
00:31:21,720 --> 00:31:22,240
Come here.

418
00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:23,360
Hurry up!

419
00:31:53,440 --> 00:31:54,520
Attack!

420
00:31:57,240 --> 00:31:59,280
Shoot them!

421
00:32:15,880 --> 00:32:16,480
What do you want to do?

422
00:32:17,480 --> 00:32:18,160
I'm warning you.

423
00:32:18,520 --> 00:32:19,160
If you kill the Magistrate,

424
00:32:19,160 --> 00:32:20,640
you will be cut into pieces.

425
00:32:37,640 --> 00:32:39,120
Now the bandits are attacking us.

426
00:32:40,160 --> 00:32:41,440
I must protect the city now.

427
00:32:43,000 --> 00:32:43,840
You hurry up and leave.

428
00:32:44,440 --> 00:32:45,400
Don't come back.

429
00:34:03,140 --> 00:34:08,580
[Tang]

430
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:57,080
Push! Harder!

431
00:34:59,040 --> 00:35:00,000
Harder!

432
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:12,160
Hurry up. Come and help!

433
00:35:50,140 --> 00:35:53,620
[Zhenxi Fortress]

434
00:39:08,800 --> 00:39:10,480
You can report it
to the military office.

435
00:39:11,280 --> 00:39:12,120
But the riot

436
00:39:12,640 --> 00:39:14,120
and the killing of Huo Huaili

437
00:39:15,040 --> 00:39:16,240
were done by me alone.

438
00:39:17,000 --> 00:39:17,840
It has nothing to do with others.

439
00:39:19,840 --> 00:39:21,720
These soldiers are guarding this place.

440
00:39:22,720 --> 00:39:24,280
They are patriotic
and loyal to the emperor.

441
00:39:25,840 --> 00:39:27,440
They have made no mistake.

